1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,849
Do something special for your family often.

2
00:00:02,880 --> 00:00:05,090
It doesn't have to be something expensive.

3
00:00:05,199 --> 00:00:07,250
It's thoughtfulness that counts.

4
00:00:07,519 --> 00:00:12,930
Anything that shows that you put your family's interests first will do the trick.

5
00:00:13,360 --> 00:00:15,410
Get the family on your team.

6
00:00:15,599 --> 00:00:17,730
Give them planned attention.

7
00:00:18,079 --> 00:00:23,570
In this busy age, a lot of people never seem able to find time for their families.

8
00:00:23,599 --> 00:00:25,890
But if we plan, we can find it.

9
00:00:26,159 --> 00:00:31,570
One company vice president told me of this method, which he says works well for him.

10
00:00:32,079 --> 00:00:39,010
My job carries a lot of responsibility, and I have no choice but to bring quite a lot of work home every night.

11
00:00:39,279 --> 00:00:44,610
But I will not neglect my family, because it's the most important thing in my life.

12
00:00:44,799 --> 00:00:47,809
It's the main reason I work as hard as I do.

13
00:00:48,159 --> 00:00:53,971
I've worked out a schedule that enables me to give attention to my family as well as to my work.

14
00:00:54,159 --> 00:00:59,730
From 7.30 to 8.30 every evening, I devote my time to my two young children.

15
00:00:59,840 --> 00:01:06,289
I play games with them, read them stories, draw, answer questions, anything they want me to do.

16
00:01:06,799 --> 00:01:13,250
After an hour with those kids of mine, they're not only satisfied, but I'm 100% fresher.

17
00:01:13,440 --> 00:01:18,369
At 8.30, they trot off to bed, and I settle down to work for two hours.

18
00:01:18,719 --> 00:01:23,090
At 10.30, I quit working and spend the next hour with my wife.

19
00:01:23,279 --> 00:01:28,050
We talk about the kids, her various activities, our plans for the future.

20
00:01:28,400 --> 00:01:33,890
This hour, undisturbed by anything, is a wonderful way to cap off the day.

21
00:01:34,719 --> 00:01:37,650
I also reserve Sundays for my family.

22
00:01:37,759 --> 00:01:39,730
The whole day is theirs.

23
00:01:40,079 --> 00:01:48,530
I find my organized program for giving my family the attention it deserves is good not only for them but also good for me.

24
00:01:48,639 --> 00:01:50,769
It gives me new energy.

25
00:01:53,279 --> 00:01:54,530
Want to make money?

